trans-unit.source: Defines methods for reading the parts of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" />.
The following example shows how to obtain a reference to an object that implements this interface.
trans-unit.target: 다음 예제에는이 인터페이스를 구현 하는 개체에 대 한 참조를 가져오는 방법을 보여 줍니다.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to obtain a <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument.FixedDocumentSequenceReader%2A> in order to access <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument> parts in an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>.
trans-unit.target: 다음 예제에서는 가져오는 방법을 보여 줍니다.는 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument.FixedDocumentSequenceReader%2A> 에 액세스 하기 위해 <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument> 파트에 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument" /> readers for each document in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument" />의 각 문서에 대해 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" /> 판독기 컬렉션을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument" /> readers, one for each document in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument" />의 각 문서에 대해 하나씩 지정되어 있는 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" /> 판독기 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentSequenceReader.FixedDocuments%2A> property to obtain a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument> readers.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하는 방법을 보여 주는 다음 예제는 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentSequenceReader.FixedDocuments%2A> 속성의 컬렉션을 가져오려면을 <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument> 판독기입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reader for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument" /> with the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
Gets the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" />, if one exists, that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument" />.
A <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> that contains the default printing options for the sequence; or <see langword="null" />, if no print ticket exists for the document.
trans-unit.target: 시퀀스의 기본 인쇄 옵션이 포함된 <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" />이거나, 문서에 대해 인쇄 티켓이 없는 경우 <see langword="null" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] sequence, see chapter 2 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 자세한 내용은 <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> 의 일부가 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] 시퀀스, 2 장 참조는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] 사양에서 가져올 수 있습니다 [XPS: 사양 및 라이선스 다운로드](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx)합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the thumbnail image, if one exists, that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence" />와 연결되어 있는 축소판 그림 이미지(있는 경우)를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> that represents the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the sequence.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> 나타내는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] 시퀀스에 대 한 합니다.
